name: TGAM - Issue 01: For the love of art
description:
Welcome to the Tannhäuser Generative Art Museum. TGAM is a space in the metaverse (https://tgam.xyz/visit) dedicated to celebrate and promulgate art made by autonomous systems (non-human) that can independently create artwork. This is a nonprofit organization made just for the love of art and supported by Tannhäuser Gate.

This first issue (For the love of art) marks the inauguration of the museum and showcases the work of Synesthesia, Marcelo Soria Rodriguez and Ismahelio.

More info: https://tgam.xyz
